{"id": "1452951234712571996", "channel_id": "1452951234712571996", "type": 0, "author_id": "1131790839291596841", "author_name": "morimensstaff01", "author_bot": false, "content": "感谢各位守密人的支持！\n《忘却前夜》OST：虚妄倒错之孕 已发布，欢迎收听、下载及分享。\n如果有基于OST的二次创作，也欢迎分享给我们！（二创请遵照同人规则，OST内容请勿商用）\n\n忘却前夜OST：虚妄倒错之孕\n父亲诞下女儿，女儿孕育父亲。\n虚妄、倒错、她所坠入的循环往复的命运。\n\n作曲：F.R.K./ B.I.A.V. Studio\n规划：B.I.A.V. Studio\n\n——◆——◆—— ◆◆◆ ——◆——◆——\n\nThank you for your support!\n\nMorimens OST: \"Pregnancy of Pervase Lies\" was released today. \nWelcome everyone to listen, download and share. If you have secondary creations based on the OST, please also share them with us!\n (Please follow the rules of the fandom for secondary creations, and do not use the OST content for commercial purposes)\n\nMorimens OST: Pregnancy of Pervase Lies\nThe Father births a Daughter. The Daughter then conceives Her Father.\nIllusion, inversion—the cyclical, ever-repeating fate into which she has fallen.\n\nComposer：F.R.K./ B.I.A.V. Studio\nPlanning：B.I.A.V. Studio", "timestamp": "2025-12-23T09:09:28.884000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [{"emoji": "scared2", "emoji_id": "1356085635374383145", "count": 12}, {"emoji": "IMG_20251113_181453", "emoji_id": "1448240235757568133", "count": 3}], "attachments": [{"id": "1452951235530326119", "filename": "OST-.png", "content_type": "image/png", "size": 1794831}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1452951571448070308", "channel_id": "1452951234712571996", "type": 0, "author_id": "1131790839291596841", "author_name": "morimensstaff01", "author_bot": false, "content": "**1. 黑月光-Black Moonlight-**\n\n睡吧，睡吧，海的婴孩，让漆黑的月光照在你沉暗的襁褓上，让千年亿年的沉梦就此沦入永恒虚妄。\n\nHush now, hush, my seaborne dear. Let the black moon cast its light upon your darkling swaddle, and sink your slumber of a billion millennia into eternal illusion.", "timestamp": "2025-12-23T09:10:49.168000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [{"id": "1452951570638569482", "filename": "1.png", "content_type": "image/png", "size": 2175331}, {"id": "1452951570936238080", "filename": "1._-Black_Moonlight-.wav", "content_type": "audio/x-wav", "size": 12087532}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1452951889934155898", "channel_id": "1452951234712571996", "type": 0, "author_id": "1131790839291596841", "author_name": "morimensstaff01", "author_bot": false, "content": "**2. 叙谎者和弦-Chord of the Lie-Teller-**\n\n这个世界一如往常，孩子依赖母亲，孩子也对母亲说谎。\n\nThe world turns as it always has: the child relies on the mother; the child lies to the mother.", "timestamp": "2025-12-23T09:12:05.101000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [{"id": "1452951888977727570", "filename": "2._-Chord_of_the_Lie-Teller-.wav", "content_type": "audio/x-wav", "size": 57141332}, {"id": "1452951889581703178", "filename": "2.png", "content_type": "image/png", "size": 2189918}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1452952084809781383", "channel_id": "1452951234712571996", "type": 0, "author_id": "1131790839291596841", "author_name": "morimensstaff01", "author_bot": false, "content": "**3. 第二面-Second Encounter-**\n\n你与许多存在都有见第二面的可能性，哪怕那是一个不应存在的婴孩，或诞生自错误的神灵。\n\nPossibilities exist for a second encounter, even with an infant that should not be, or a god born from an error.", "timestamp": "2025-12-23T09:12:51.563000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": "2025-12-31T10:15:17.336000+00:00", "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [{"id": "1452952084176437258", "filename": "3.png", "content_type": "image/png", "size": 2175891}, {"id": "1452952084516442154", "filename": "3._-Second_Encounter-.wav", "content_type": "audio/x-wav", "size": 40816380}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1452952185955418243", "channel_id": "1452951234712571996", "type": 0, "author_id": "1131790839291596841", "author_name": "morimensstaff01", "author_bot": false, "content": "**4. 假脐带-False Umbilical Cord-**\n\n你没来得及救她，这个她没有逃出来。\n她被分食，她孤立无援，她拴上了一条假脐带。\n\nYou were too late. This version of her couldn't escape.\nShe was partitioned and devoured; she stood helplessly alone, tethered to a false umbilical cord.", "timestamp": "2025-12-23T09:13:15.678000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [{"id": "1452952184927813632", "filename": "4._-False_Umbilical_Cord-.wav", "content_type": "audio/x-wav", "size": 31830648}, {"id": "1452952185485660210", "filename": "4.png", "content_type": "image/png", "size": 2179426}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1452952381846196337", "channel_id": "1452951234712571996", "type": 0, "author_id": "1131790839291596841", "author_name": "morimensstaff01", "author_bot": false, "content": "**5. 雪松-Cedar-**\n\n你要怎么描述一位在太耀眼时离别的同行者？\n不要描述他的耀眼，描述他的手臂，描述你在他身上闻到的雪松香气。\n\nHow would you describe a companion who left at the height of his radiance?\nDo not speak of his brilliance. Describe the cold metal of his arm; describe the cedar fragrance that lingered in his wake.", "timestamp": "2025-12-23T09:14:02.382000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [{"id": "1452952380986622022", "filename": "5.png", "content_type": "image/png", "size": 2164706}, {"id": "1452952381854580797", "filename": "5._-Cedar-.wav", "content_type": "audio/x-wav", "size": 30499896}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1452952524964237324", "channel_id": "1452951234712571996", "type": 0, "author_id": "1131790839291596841", "author_name": "morimensstaff01", "author_bot": false, "content": "**6. 某一个结局-One Possible Ending-**\n\n你又来晚了一些，别停留，再快，再快一点。\n快赶往下一个结局。\n\nAgain, you were too late. Do not linger. Faster, faster still.\nHurry toward the next ending.", "timestamp": "2025-12-23T09:14:36.504000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [{"id": "1452952524196675594", "filename": "6._-One_Possible_Ending-.wav", "content_type": "audio/x-wav", "size": 25178666}, {"id": "1452952524704321639", "filename": "6.png", "content_type": "image/png", "size": 2181373}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1452952704824381451", "channel_id": "1452951234712571996", "type": 0, "author_id": "1131790839291596841", "author_name": "morimensstaff01", "author_bot": false, "content": "**7. 家-Home-**\n\n她和她有她和她的虔诚，他和他有他和他的反叛和忠心。\n她编织一个弥天大谎，他和他和她和她陪她演戏。\n家，大家组成了甜蜜而不可分割的家。\n\nShe and She each have their own devotions; He and He each hold their own rebellion and loyalty.\nShe weaved a colossal lie; He and He and She and She all chose to act their parts.\nHome. Everyone together formed a sweet, inseparable home.", "timestamp": "2025-12-23T09:15:19.386000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [{"id": "1452952704380047503", "filename": "7.png", "content_type": "image/png", "size": 2156044}, {"id": "1452952704656605225", "filename": "7._-Home-.wav", "content_type": "audio/x-wav", "size": 17912602}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1452952863440502957", "channel_id": "1452951234712571996", "type": 0, "author_id": "1131790839291596841", "author_name": "morimensstaff01", "author_bot": false, "content": "**8. 海国-Lemuria-**\n\n让我们呼唤那由海中上浮的神国的名字——利莫里亚，利莫里亚。\n\nLet us call upon the name of the Divine Realm that rises from the sea—Lemuria, Lemuria.", "timestamp": "2025-12-23T09:15:57.203000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [{"id": "1452952862404513853", "filename": "8._-Lemuria-.wav", "content_type": "audio/x-wav", "size": 29395024}, {"id": "1452952863037722695", "filename": "8.png", "content_type": "image/png", "size": 2161795}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1452953442636136529", "channel_id": "1452951234712571996", "type": 0, "author_id": "1131790839291596841", "author_name": "morimensstaff01", "author_bot": false, "content": "**9. 回到原点-Return to Origin-**\n\n什么比死亡和疼痛更可怕？\n这对你来说不算一个难以解答的问题。\n\nWhat is more terrible than death and pain?\nFor you, this is not a difficult question.", "timestamp": "2025-12-23T09:18:15.294000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [{"id": "1452953441818378342", "filename": "9.png", "content_type": "image/png", "size": 2179529}, {"id": "1452953442396930244", "filename": "9._-Return_to_Origin-.wav", "content_type": "audio/x-wav", "size": 62368288}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1452953583405502616", "channel_id": "1452951234712571996", "type": 0, "author_id": "1131790839291596841", "author_name": "morimensstaff01", "author_bot": false, "content": "**10. 秘密流亡-Secret Exile-**\n\n逃跑吧，两条鱼跃入了水面。\n它们暂时抛却了一切，试图瞒着世界与彼此相伴流亡。\n\nLet's run. Two fish leap into the water.\nFor a moment, they cast everything aside, trying to flee the world and wander into exile side by side.", "timestamp": "2025-12-23T09:18:48.856000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [{"id": "1452953582688014417", "filename": "10._-Secret_Exile-.wav", "content_type": "audio/x-wav", "size": 51714794}, {"id": "1452953583245983887", "filename": "10.png", "content_type": "image/png", "size": 2184495}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1452953726720540784", "channel_id": "1452951234712571996", "type": 0, "author_id": "1131790839291596841", "author_name": "morimensstaff01", "author_bot": false, "content": "**11. 她与他与祂之死-Her, His, and Its Death-**\n\n哦……原来还有更坏的结局。\n\nOh... so there exists an even worse ending.", "timestamp": "2025-12-23T09:19:23.025000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [{"id": "1452953726091268242", "filename": "11.png", "content_type": "image/png", "size": 2181197}, {"id": "1452953726380806270", "filename": "11._-Her_His_and_Its_Death-.wav", "content_type": "audio/x-wav", "size": 19919526}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1452953914931548220", "channel_id": "1452951234712571996", "type": 0, "author_id": "1131790839291596841", "author_name": "morimensstaff01", "author_bot": false, "content": "**12. 面团盾牌-Dough Shield-**\n\n她与现实之间，她与虚妄之间，竖起了一面小小的盾牌。\n面粉、鸡蛋、柠檬、蜂蜜、糖、泡打粉、黄油烘烤成的盾牌。\n\nBetween her and reality, between her and illusion, a small shield has been raised:\nA shield baked from flour, eggs, lemon, honey, sugar, baking powder, and butter.", "timestamp": "2025-12-23T09:20:07.898000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [{"id": "1452953914004606987", "filename": "12._-Dough_Shield-.wav", "content_type": "audio/x-wav", "size": 33925856}, {"id": "1452953914583416852", "filename": "12.png", "content_type": "image/png", "size": 2178995}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1452954136424484947", "channel_id": "1452951234712571996", "type": 0, "author_id": "1131790839291596841", "author_name": "morimensstaff01", "author_bot": false, "content": "**13. 在黎明时告别-Farewell at Dawn-**\n\n天空将要亮了，让我们作别昨日。\n作别昨日的苦痛、荒诞、迷惘，\n迎接一个更明亮的，天各一方的明天。\n\nThe sky is about to brighten. Let us bid farewell to yesterday.\nFarewell to yesterday’s suffering, absurdity, and confusion, and welcome a brighter tomorrow where we each go our separate ways.", "timestamp": "2025-12-23T09:21:00.706000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [{"id": "1452954135367516242", "filename": "13.png", "content_type": "image/png", "size": 2184248}, {"id": "1452954135908319254", "filename": "13._-Farewell_at_Dawn-.wav", "content_type": "audio/x-wav", "size": 18554160}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1452954335397810206", "channel_id": "1452951234712571996", "type": 0, "author_id": "1131790839291596841", "author_name": "morimensstaff01", "author_bot": false, "content": "**14. 腐神明-The Rotting Deity-**\n\n神诞生的第七日。\n哦，神啊，神啊……\n不过是荒谬的错误与虚假的谎言。\n\nDay seven after god's birth.\nGod, oh god...\nYou're nothing but a ludicrous error, a false lie.", "timestamp": "2025-12-23T09:21:48.145000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [{"id": "1452954334504554652", "filename": "14._-The_Rotting_Deity-.wav", "content_type": "audio/x-wav", "size": 77113498}, {"id": "1452954335066456115", "filename": "14.png", "content_type": "image/png", "size": 2176913}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1452954525756424222", "channel_id": "1452951234712571996", "type": 0, "author_id": "1131790839291596841", "author_name": "morimensstaff01", "author_bot": false, "content": "**15. 「3.14159▼▼▼▼」**\n\n3.14159▼▼，3.141592▼▼▼，3.14159265▼▼▼▼……\n雪地里永无终结的圆，残忍的、永远不会结束的圆周率。\n\n3.14159▼▼, 3.141592▼▼▼, 3.14159265▼▼▼▼…\nIt's an endless circle in the snow, a cruel, never-ending Pi.", "timestamp": "2025-12-23T09:22:33.530000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [{"id": "1452954525215490070", "filename": "15.png", "content_type": "image/png", "size": 2169262}, {"id": "1452954525483663410", "filename": "15._3.14159.wav", "content_type": "audio/x-wav", "size": 57993240}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1452954686901719051", "channel_id": "1452951234712571996", "type": 0, "author_id": "1131790839291596841", "author_name": "morimensstaff01", "author_bot": false, "content": "**16. 甜蜜乐园-Sweet Paradise-**\n\n孩童并不属于母亲，祂已打定主意，所有人都要留在这里。\n留在祂永恒延续的甜蜜乐园。\n\nThe child does not belong to the mother. \"He\" has made up His mind: everyone must stay here.\nStay in His eternally enduring, sweet paradise.", "timestamp": "2025-12-23T09:23:11.950000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [{"id": "1452954686100475986", "filename": "16._-Sweet_Paradise-.mp3", "content_type": "audio/mpeg", "size": 7876443}, {"id": "1452954686612308101", "filename": "16.png", "content_type": "image/png", "size": 2184925}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1452954898353360927", "channel_id": "1452951234712571996", "type": 0, "author_id": "1131790839291596841", "author_name": "morimensstaff01", "author_bot": false, "content": "**17. 坠下-The Fall-**\n\n在旅途的尽头，你知道有谁在等待你。\n但你还没能逃离，你从高空中再次坠下。\n\nA certain someone is waiting for you at the end of your journey. You know it by heart.\nBut you have not yet escaped. Once more you fall from the heights.", "timestamp": "2025-12-23T09:24:02.364000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [{"id": "1452954897765892188", "filename": "17.png", "content_type": "image/png", "size": 2158607}, {"id": "1452954898063691848", "filename": "17._-The_Fall-.wav", "content_type": "audio/x-wav", "size": 37020618}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1452955093031981056", "channel_id": "1452951234712571996", "type": 0, "author_id": "1131790839291596841", "author_name": "morimensstaff01", "author_bot": false, "content": "**18. 在祂女儿黑暗的子宫中-In His Daughter's Darkling Womb-**\n\n拥抱我吧，我的宝贝，我的……父亲，我的命运。\n\nEmbrace me, my dear baby, my dear… father, my destiny.", "timestamp": "2025-12-23T09:24:48.779000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [{"id": "1452955092054573170", "filename": "18._-In_His_Daughters_Darkling_Womb-.wav", "content_type": "audio/x-wav", "size": 59880092}, {"id": "1452955092750696509", "filename": "18.png", "content_type": "image/png", "size": 2180226}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1452955130587512842", "channel_id": "1452951234712571996", "type": 0, "author_id": "1131790839291596841", "author_name": "morimensstaff01", "author_bot": false, "content": "<:IMG_20251113_181453:1448240235757568133> 以上就是本次OST的全部曲目~\nThe above are all the tracks of this OST~", "timestamp": "2025-12-23T09:24:57.733000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [{"emoji": "IMG_20251113_181453", "emoji_id": "1448240235757568133", "count": 10}], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
